Counterweight	KEY:Anvil Trick ~ Counterweight	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:You can use your anvil as a counterweight when you climb a rope or chain to reduce your Climb DC by 5.																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.14
Improve Armor	KEY:Anvil Trick ~ Improve Armor	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:You can spend an hour with your anvil and a suit of nonmagical metal armor to temporarily increase the armor's armor bonus by 1. This bonus ends after the next time the wearer is hit.																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.14
Quick Fix		KEY:Anvil Trick ~ Quick Fix		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:You can spend 1 minute to remove the broken condition from a metal the item for 1 hour. At the end of the hour it regains the broken condition and loses an additional 1d6 hit points (unless properly fixed by then).																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.14
Smash Through	KEY:Anvil Trick ~ Smash Through	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:When you end your move adjacent to a closed door, you can open the door as part of your move action (instead of as a separate move action) by smashing it with an anvil as you move. If the door is stuck or locked, you must succeed at a bull rush combat maneuver check that exceeds the door's break DC.																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.14
